#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/getting-started.md:66
msgid "Premium pricing but excellent quality"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/getting-started.md:68
msgid "[Unstable]**Kimi K2** (`k2`): Moonshot's cost-effective model"
